  <brief_title>Evaluation of Bioresorbable Sheet to Prevent Intra-Abdominal Adhesions in Colorectal Surgeries</brief_title>
  <official_title>Evaluation of Intra-Abdominal Adhesions in Ileostomy Procedures When Using a Resorbable Polylactide Film (SurgiWrap) in Colorectal Surgeries</official_title>
  <sponsors>
